These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: colombian, mexican
2 different pets are kept: cat, hamster
City: berlin, miami
1. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
2. the mexican is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Nationality   | mexican    | colombian |
| Pet         | hamster | cat    |
| City     | berlin     | miami      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, sprite
There 2 different types of food: pumpkin, strawberry
There are 2 different favourite colors: blood-red, coral
1. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person eating pumpkin is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Beverage      | sprite  | mirinda   |
| Food   | strawberry | pumpkin  |
| Color     | coral   | blood-red |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: fuchsia, coral
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, martial-arts
There are 2 different favourite beverages: tea, water
1. the person who likes coral is in an even position##4
2. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Color         | fuchsia   | coral  |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | fantasy  |
| Beverage         | tea   | water |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-4::.
There 2 different types of food: pomegranate, raspberry
The people have 2 different jobs:  mechanic, dancer
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, cain
1. the prince-smoker is on the right of the dancer##1
2. the person eating pomegranate is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Food          | pomegranate | raspberry |
| Job   | dancer   | mechanic   |
| Cigar     | cain       | prince      |

