.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-5::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: disaster, martial-arts
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cricket, rugby
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, november
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |
| Movie-Genre        | disaster      | martial-arts  |
| Sport       | rugby     | cricket    |
| Birthday   | march | november |

