.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
There 2 different types of food: pepper, radish
City: liverpool, marseilles
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, soul
1. the fan of soul is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
2. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
3. the person eating pepper is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | radish | pepper     |
| City     | marseilles | liverpool |
| Music-Genre   | soul | punk    |

 #################################

 
