2. the owner of the ferret is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the fish is on the right of the coach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |  2   |
| Job           | coach     | chef |
| Pet   | ferret | fish  |
| Nationality     | egyptian      | dutch |

