.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-15::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skateboarding, water-polo
There are 2 different nationalities: colombian, indian
There are 2 different favourite beverages: water, 7up
1. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking water##1
2. the colombian is on the left of the indian##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Sport         | water-polo | skateboarding |
| Nationality   | colombian     | indian     |
| Beverage           | 7up          | water     |

